{"analytics_identifier":"OT1065","base_path":"/government/organisations/reserve-forces-and-cadets-associations","content_id":"88df8ced-89b1-4d95-9b6a-72d1d4f324a8","description":"We give advice and assistance to the Defence Council, and to the army, navy and air force on matters that concern reserves and cadets. Reserve Forces' and Cadets' Associations (RFCA) works with the Ministry of Defence .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We give advice and assistance to the Defence Council, and to the army, navy and air force on matters that concern reserves and cadets.</p>\n\n<p>Reserve Forces' and Cadets' Associations (RFCA) works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence\">Ministry of Defence</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-defence","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"mod","formatted_title":"Reserve Forces&#39; <br/>and Cadets&#39; <br/>Associations"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/reserve-forces-and-cadets-associations/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/reserve-forces-and-cadets-associations/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/mars-uk-signs-armed-forces-covenant-to-support-military-community","image":{"alt_text":"Lt Col Tom Spencer-Smith, Commanding Officer, 1st Battalion Grenadier Guards and Defence's co-signatory of the Covenant, with Luke Bellinger, Director of Strategic Sourcing at Mars UK, and Mars UK representatives. Copyright: Mars UK.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68d3babd8c739d679fb1dccc/s712_MARS_Picture_AFC.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68d3babdc908572e81248bfc/s465_MARS_Picture_AFC.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68d3babdb6c608ff9421b237/MARS_Picture_AFC.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-09-24T10:26:34.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Mars UK has pledged its commitment to supporting the military community by signing the Armed Forces Covenant.</p>\n</div>","title":"Mars UK signs Armed Forces Covenant to support military community"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/over-200-employers-recognised-with-defence-employer-recognition-scheme-gold-award-for-outstanding-support-to-the-armed-forces-community","image":{"alt_text":"Employers and reservists at an employer engagement event hosted by the British Army. Copyright: RFCA.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/687e072bec877ce6a9f9c672/s712_RFCA_Gold_25.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/687e072b42e4d134c440e528/s465_RFCA_Gold_25.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/687e072b42e4d134c440e529/RFCA_Gold_25.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-07-21T00:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Employers from several industries have been recognised for their exceptional support to the armed forces community with the Gold Defence Employer Recognition Scheme (ERS) Award.</p>\n</div>","title":"Over 200 employers recognised with Defence Employer Recognition Scheme Gold Award for outstanding support to the armed forces community"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/employers-recognised-for-their-defence-support-with-2025-ers-silver-awards","image":{"alt_text":"Silver ERS winners 2024. Copyright: RFCA.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/684fdd7cdf3ce2ce31e3fa42/s712_2024_ERS_Silver_Award_winners.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/684fdd7c72e2ed81c07970e9/s465_2024_ERS_Silver_Award_winners.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/684fdd7c19e3b84158cba38c/2024_ERS_Silver_Award_winners.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-06-16T10:00:01.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Ministry of Defence is pleased to announce that 307 organisations have been awarded the Defence Employer Recognition Scheme (ERS) Silver Award for 2025.</p>\n</div>","title":"Employers recognised for their defence support with 2025 ERS Silver Awards"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/rfca-conference-highlights-the-integral-role-of-reserves-and-cadets-in-national-defence","image":{"alt_text":"The audience at the RFCA conference addressed by the Minister for Veterans and People, Alistair Carns OBE MC MP. Copyright: Kevin Poolman, DRM.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/673b3a9f49ce28002166a962/s712_GOV_UK_Featured.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/673b3a9f72f19089dfdadeaf/s465_GOV_UK_Featured.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/673b3a9ffc572967fe66a955/GOV_UK_Featured.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2024-11-18T12:59:02.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The 2024 RFCA conference focussed on the vital contribution of the RFCA network in connecting defence and broader society.</p>\n</div>","title":"RFCA conference highlights the integral role of reserves and cadets in national defence"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/support-and-benefits-for-reservists-and-their-families","image":{"alt_text":"Royal Naval Physical Training instructor from the Royal Navy School of Physical Training (RNSPT) and his family walking on Portsmouth Beach. MOD Crown Copyright.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66d9d4f1561701fa1c214ead/s712_RNSPT_Portsmouth.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66d9d4f1561701fa1c214eac/s465_RNSPT_Portsmouth.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66d9d4f1e87ad2f121826510/RNSPT_Portsmouth.png"},"public_updated_at":"2024-08-29T09:30:03